OL,3,COver 50,000 visitors expected at Isle
OL,4,Cof Man TT as police launch safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FPolice in the Isle of Man are urging
OL,8,Fpeople to 'know their limits' when
OL,9,Fvisiting the island for the world-
OL,10,Ffamous TT races later this month.
OL,12,FMore than 50,000 tourists are expected
OL,13,Fto travel to the island to watch the
OL,14,Fracing fortnight, starting at the end
OL,15,Fof the month.
OL,17,FChief Constable Russ Foster gave a
OL,18,Fpress briefing, highlighting where the
OL,19,Fconstabulary will be focusing their
OL,20,Fefforts for the racing fortnight.
