OL,3,COver 50,000 visitors expected at Isle
OL,4,Cof Man TT as police launch safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FHe said: "We're asking that people
OL,8,Fride within their limits so they
OL,9,Funderstand their own ability and ride
OL,10,Fto the road conditions."
OL,12,FIt forms part of the annual 'Know Your
OL,13,FLimits' campaign by the Isle of Man
OL,14,FConstabulary, to increase safety on
OL,15,Fthe island's roads during TT.
OL,17,FThe TT races attract fans from all
OL,18,Fover the world, with a particular
OL,19,Fincrease in people travelling from
OL,20,FNorth America.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
