OL,3,COver 50,000 visitors expected at Isle
OL,4,Cof Man TT as police launch safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FThis follows two incidents in 2024
OL,8,Fwhich involved international riders
OL,9,Ftravelling on the right side of the
OL,10,Froad.
OL,12,FMr Foster concluded: "We adopt a
OL,13,Fpolicing style that's very much firm
OL,14,Fbut fair - we're intolerant of crime
OL,15,Fand anti-social behaviour - we will
OL,16,Fintervene early, we will conduct a
OL,17,Ffull investigation, and we will put
OL,18,Fpeople before the next available
OL,19,Fcourt."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
